node.text:
Supreme®/Clarks Originals®. 09/09/2021

This Fall, Supreme has worked with Clarks Originals® on a custom version of the Wallabee®. 

The shoe features a premium suede upper with woven pattern, leather lining and natural crepe sole. Made exclusively for Supreme, the Wallabee® will be offered in four color ways. 

Available September 9th. 

Available in Japan September 11th.

Supreme®/New York Yankees®. 09/02/2021

Supreme has worked with MLB on a collection featuring the New York Yankees™ logo. The collection features a GORE-TEX 700-Fill Down Jacket, Track Jacket, Denim Trucker Jacket, S/S Top, Hooded Sweatshirt, Track Pant, Jean, Sweatpant, New Era® Fitted Hat, New Era® Beanie and Skateboard. 

Select pieces available September 2nd. 

Select pieces available in Japan September 4th.
